Module AppointmentScheduler
Package Application.Controllers

Class AddAppointmentController

java.lang.Object
Application.Controllers.AddAppointmentController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class AddAppointmentController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
The AddAppointmentController which is responsible for the logic behind AddAppointmentView. It helps provide I/O functionality and acts as an interface between the front end GUI and backend database and provides user data validation, error handling and local cache storage for creating new Appointment POJOs.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Michael Short
